    "title": "十分钟入门 CLAUDE CODE ",
    "preview_text": "十分钟入门 CLAUDE CODE\n你不需要会写代码，不需要懂命令行，甚至不需要知道什么是 Terminal。你只需要 10 分钟，就能用上目前地球上最强的 AI 工具之一。\n先讲一个真实的故事",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFObFOYbEAAh_MW.jpg",
    "content_state": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4q92v",
          "text": "十分钟入门 CLAUDE CODE",
          "type": "blockquote"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "afmn6",
          "text": "你不需要会写代码，不需要懂命令行，甚至不需要知道什么是 Terminal。你只需要 10 分钟，就能用上目前地球上最强的 AI 工具之一。",
          "type": "blockquote"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "26nf9",
          "text": "先讲一个真实的故事",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2g37j",
          "text": "我老婆，技术很菜，命令行也不太会用。2023年我推荐她用 ChatGPT，她很震惊，还用ChatGPT 帮她搞定了推荐信。  ",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3hok4",
          "text": "我教了她很多年的CLI，她就是学不会，不是会学不会，实际上是没有使用的习惯，今年初我帮她安装了 Claude Code，教了她 10 分钟基本操作，她再次被震惊。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2tpl7",
          "text": "像我老婆这样的人用户实在太多了， 所以我觉得很有必要把这么好用的工具教给你们。  ",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 16,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "eat4p",
          "text": "AI 不再是程序员的专属玩具了。 它正在变成像 Word、Excel 一样的生产力工具——区别在于，它的能力上限比 Word 和 Excel 高出几个数量级。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4n228",
          "text": "CLAUDE CODE 是什么？一句话解释",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 6,
              "offset": 48,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "p8j1",
          "text": "Claude Code 是 Anthropic 公司（Claude AI 的制造商）推出的一个 AI 工作台。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "br5tv",
          "text": "你可以把它理解为一个住在你电脑里的超级助手：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 9,
              "offset": 2,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "5madl",
          "text": "它能读写你电脑上的文件——帮你整理文档、批量改名、分析数据",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 4,
              "offset": 2,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "7q2j8",
          "text": "它能上网搜索——帮你做调研、找资料、追踪热点",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 7,
              "offset": 2,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "65ar9",
          "text": "它能安装各种技能包——做 PPT、生成图片、写推文、创建视频、分析 Excel",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 6,
              "offset": 3,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "ca9od",
          "text": "它拥有百万级记忆力——一次对话里可以处理相当于一本书的信息量",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 18,
              "offset": 37,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "3uj7h",
          "text": "跟 ChatGPT 的网页对话框比，Claude Code 最大的区别是：它不只是跟你聊天，它能直接帮你干活。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9g4gp",
          "text": "ChatGPT 像一个坐在屏幕里的顾问——你问它，它答你，但活还是你自己干。Claude Code 像一个坐在你旁边的全能助手——你说一句，它直接帮你把事情做了，结果文件就在你的电脑上。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "d2vfb",
          "text": "在开始之前，你需要什么？",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 3,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "fir5",
          "text": "硬件： 一台能上网的电脑（Mac、Windows、Linux 都行）",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 3,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "77bh9",
          "text": "软件： 不需要提前装任何东西，下面会一步步教你",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "urls": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 93,
                "text": "claude.ai",
                "toIndex": 102
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 0,
              "length": 9,
              "offset": 93
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 3,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "d25iq",
          "text": "费用： Claude Code 需要订阅 Claude Pro（每月 $20）或 Claude Max（每月 $100）。Pro 计划足够日常使用。如果你还没有 Claude 账号，去 claude.ai 注册一个。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 5,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "dvljq",
          "text": "技术基础： 零。真的是零。你只要会打字就行。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7kncu",
          "text": "第一步：安装 CLAUDE CODE（3 分钟）",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "em6co",
          "text": "方法一：桌面应用（最简单，推荐新手）",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2krau",
          "text": "Claude Code 现在有桌面应用了，安装跟装微信一样简单：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "urls": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 3,
                "text": "claude.ai/code",
                "toIndex": 17
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 1,
              "length": 14,
              "offset": 3
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8ktcc",
          "text": "打开 claude.ai/code",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dnkot",
          "text": "下载对应你系统的安装包（Mac 或 Windows）",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ft0d5",
          "text": "双击安装，打开应用",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1tb5t",
          "text": "用你的 Claude 账号登录",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1avm5",
          "text": "搞定。没有命令行，没有配置，开箱即用。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 2,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "f5tuh",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "cj19q",
          "text": "方法二：命令行安装（适合想多了解一点的人）",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "5gm8v",
          "text": "如果你想用命令行版本（功能完全一样，只是界面不同），需要先装一个叫 Node.js 的东西。别怕，跟着做就行：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 14,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "707vl",
          "text": "第一步：安装 Node.js",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "urls": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 2,
                "text": "nodejs.org",
                "toIndex": 12
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 3,
              "length": 10,
              "offset": 2
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "so62",
          "text": "去 nodejs.org 下载\"LTS\"版本（左边那个绿色按钮），双击安装，一路点\"下一步\"就行。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 4,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6bcup",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 18,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "5b7l8",
          "text": "第二步：安装 Claude Code",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 6,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "71g4t",
          "text": "Mac 用户：打开\"终端\"（在启动台搜索\"终端\"或\"Terminal\"）",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 10,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "f3adu",
          "text": "Windows 用户：打开\"命令提示符\"或\"PowerShell\"（按 Win 键搜索即可）",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 5,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7qq5l",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6ordj",
          "text": "输入这一行命令，然后按回车：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "mentions": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 15,
                "text": "anthropic",
                "toIndex": 25
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "csfbi",
          "text": "npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ad708",
          "text": "等它跑完（通常不到一分钟），再输入：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3btbe",
          "text": "claude",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "31a7q",
          "text": "第一次运行会让你登录 Claude 账号，按提示操作就行。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3nnir",
          "text": "看到欢迎界面？恭喜，你已经装好了。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 6,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1ehbm",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "csqnv",
          "text": "方法三：网页版（零安装）",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "62t30",
          "text": "如果你连安装都不想搞，可以直接在浏览器里用：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "urls": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 3,
                "text": "claude.ai/code",
                "toIndex": 17
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 7,
              "length": 14,
              "offset": 3
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9dbea",
          "text": "打开 claude.ai/code",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1rkgk",
          "text": "选择 \"Web\" 版本",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1uv8d",
          "text": "直接开始用",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3dtcs",
          "text": "网页版功能会少一些（比如不能直接操作你电脑上的文件），但用来体验和学习完全足够。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "5avcq",
          "text": "第二步：你的第一次对话（2 分钟）",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "cdvp1",
          "text": "打开 Claude Code 后，你会看到一个输入框。就像跟朋友发消息一样，直接打字就行。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7na5",
          "text": "试试这个：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 8,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fj1dr",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1g9l6",
          "text": "按回车，等几秒钟。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6ajal",
          "text": "你会看到 Claude Code 直接帮你写好了一篇自我介绍——而且它不是那种一眼就能看出是 AI 写的八股文，而是会根据你给的信息来定制内容。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 23,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "7drgs",
          "text": "恭喜，你已经在用 Claude Code 了。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3k8gf",
          "text": "再试一个：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 9,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4nmkp",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "d3sdd",
          "text": "这次 Claude Code 不但帮你做了分析，还把结果保存成了一个文件。你可以在你的电脑上直接打开它。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
