              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "9ecsl",
          "text": "下周：探索 Skills 技能包，找到 2-3 个最适合你工作场景的技能",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 4,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "2rth8",
          "text": "一个月后：建立你自己的工作流——固定的 Prompt 模板、常用的指令集",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "aqo4a",
          "text": "从\"会用\"到\"用好\"，中间差的就是几周的实践。",
